(registered 2019-07-08)

Name: Ronald Jacobs

Email: ron.jacobs&shopkick.com

Media type name: application

Media subtype name: vnd.shopkick+json

Required parameters: version=n

   The parameter value is a non-negative integer with semantics that 
   are internal at this time. The parameter is required as the 
   primary purpose of this media type is to specify a version and the
   inability to do so would be indicated by using the 
   application/json media type instead of this media type.

Optional parameters: N/A

Encoding considerations: binary

   application/json as defined in RFC 7159 Section 12. No executable 
   content should be included, integrity or confidentiality
